        "markdown": "## Step 4: Switch Surfaces\n\nAction:\n- Use the view selector on the sample node.\n- Switch through `Detail`, `Summary`, and `Icon` surfaces.\n\nResult:\n- [ ] PASS\n- [ ] FAIL\n\nNotes:"
      }
